window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The truth is coming. The end is near....&nbsp;&nbsp;</p> <p>With Earth in chaos and life on New Kerguelen shaken like never before, a discovery on the mysterious world of Sanctuary blows apart humanity's understanding of just about everything.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p> <p>The consequences are almost unfathomable, the urgency unprecedented, and the revelations of a kind that even Dan McCarthy isn't ready for.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p> <p>One way or another, nothing will ever be the same. And this time, it's final....</p>"; 
